						               													<description>Everyone likes different things, sees things differently.&amp;#10;Can you pick a theme, then split everyone evenly?&amp;#10;Get them to choose exactly 50/50 to score points!&amp;#10;Let&amp;rsquo;s find out what they really like!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You can play online, or with listeners on the streaming site.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This game is only for Japanese OTAKU. Because of many Japanese idioms and similar in the game, this edition will not be translated into English, and is only available in Japanese.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player has one Voting card, with an A on one side, and B on the other.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The lead player reads the top of the topic card for example, Animation. They then make two selections, for example A: Dragon Ball or B: One Piece.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Each player included in the round then votes A or B secretly, and all votes are revealed at once. Players may not lie about their selections.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;If the votes are 50/50, the lead player takes the topic card and scores a point.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;At the end of the game, the winner is the player with the most points.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You will all learn what the secret likings of the players are!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
